        onSkip: { zh: "周长 = $\\pi d$ 或 $2\\pi r$。面积 = $\\pi r^2$。看单位区分。", en: "Circumference = $\\pi d$ or $2\\pi r$. Area = $\\pi r^2$. Distinguish by units." },
