        onSkip: { zh: "球：SA = $4\\pi r^2$（$r^2$ = 面积），V = $\\frac{4}{3}\\pi r^3$（$r^3$ = 体积）。", en: "Sphere: SA = $4\\pi r^2$ ($r^2$ = area), V = $\\frac{4}{3}\\pi r^3$ ($r^3$ = volume)." },
